  "title": "Operating Theatre Staff Nurse / Senior Staff Nurse #HJO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide pre-, intra-, and post-operative nursing care in accordance with established standards and protocols.</li>\n  <li>Assist surgeons and anaesthetists during operations, ensuring patient safety and aseptic practices at all times.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and maintain the operating room, instruments, and equipment before, during, and after procedures.</li>\n  <li>Monitor patients’ conditions and respond promptly to clinical changes.</li>\n  <li>Participate in continuous quality improvement, infection control, and patient safety initiatives.</li>\n  <li>Supervise and guide junior nurses and support staff where required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Nursing from a recognised institution.</li>\n  <li>Registered with the Singapore Nursing Board (SNB).</li>\n  <li>Preferably with relevant experience in Operating Theatre nursing; training will be provided for new entrants.</li>\n  <li>Strong teamwork, communication, and critical thinking skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p><br></p>",
